                       <td>(IntOpt) HTTP port to connect to Nexenta REST API server</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                       <td>nexenta_rest_protocol = auto</td>
                       <td>(StrOpt) Use http or https for REST connection (default auto)</td>
